  @"args": @{
    @"deepLink": @"msteams://attacker.com/malicious"
  }
};
// Send via XPC to notificationcenter service
```

The service has **no caller validation** and directly processes the deep link.

---

## Why These Work

- **Finding 1 & 2**: No origin checks or incomplete lockdown.
- **Finding 3**: Whitelist is remotely configurable, not hardcoded.
- **Finding 4**: XPC services accept any caller without validation.

